      • testHybridLibrarySearch

        public static void testHybridLibrarySearch(int minScan,
                           int maxScan)
        This is an experimental method still under development. In addition to spectral similarity measures this method also compute the match statistics usually used in PSM matches in database search (e.g. percent b/y, explained intensity etc...) SVM can then be used to learn a model that combined spectral-library searhc an database matches features to better filter out false positives
        Parameters:
        minScan -
        maxScan -
